descriptionHtml:
[center][size=4]Barbiana is one of my presets.[/size]

[size=4]She will be used as an upcoming Follower, the author of the follower will be announced later.[/size]

[size=4]To make Barbiana appear as in the images you will need the following mods.
[/size]
[size=4]Race: Nord[/size]
[size=4]True Eyes : Human Green Nebula[/size]
[size=4]KS Hairdos : 0Dawn[/size]
[size=4]Demoniac Skin texture[/size]
[size=4]Brow : vanilla skyrim human 7

[/size][size=5]Installation:
[/size][size=4]Drop the .jslot file into your SKSE/pluggins/Chargen/Presets folder[/size]

[size=2]Credits
True Eyes
KS Hairdos-Renewal
Demoniac Skin Texture[/size][/center]
author: Tushani
